      },
      "block_id": "real_general_003_textile_application_flow_b001",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          295.20001220703125,
          780.751953125,
          300.1750183105469,
          794.1347045898438
        ],
        "page": 1
      },
      "text": "1",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_003_textile_application_flow_b002",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          90.0,
          79.70794677734375,
          121.90939331054688,
          95.8971939086914
        ],
        "page": 1
      },
      "text": "附件",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 18.0
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_003_textile_application_flow_b003",
      "level": 1,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          178.44000244140625,
          139.36399841308594,
          416.8800048828125,
          160.44200134277344
        ],
        "page": 1
      },
      "text": "2025 年度十大类纺织创新精品",
      "type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 18.0
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_003_textile_application_flow_b004",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          171.60000610351562,
          170.56399536132812,
          423.6000061035156,
          191.64199829101562
        ],
        "page": 1
      },
      "text": "建设推广工作网上申报流程说明",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_003_textile_application_flow_b005",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          122.04000091552734,
          235.70794677734375,
          225.9493865966797,
          251.89720153808594
        ],
        "page": 1
      },
      "text": "一、登录/注册",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_003_textile_application_flow_b006",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          122.04000091552734,
          264.0369567871094,
          505.3089599609375,
          285.4897155761719
        ],
        "page": 1
      },
      "text": "进入2025 年度十大类纺织创新精品建设推广申报系统",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_003_textile_application_flow_b007",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          90.0,
          295.2369384765625,
          513.22998046875,
          316.689697265625
        ],
        "page": 1
      },
      "text": "（http://topten.ctic.org.cn）后，通过“申报入口”进行注册登录。",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_003_textile_application_flow_b008",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          122.04000091552734,
          329.3079528808594,
          266.0260925292969,
          345.4971923828125
        ],
        "page": 1
      },
      "text": "二、企业及产品信息",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_003_textile_application_flow_b009",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          122.04000091552734,
          357.636962890625,
          513.22998046875,
          379.0897216796875
        ],
        "page": 1
      },
      "text": "点击左侧导航栏的“申报指南”按钮，点击“去申报项目”，",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_003_textile_application_flow_b010",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          90.0,
          388.8369445800781,
          505.3097229003906,
          410.2897033691406
        ],
        "page": 1
      },
      "text": "填写申报企业和产品基本信息，在“申报产品基本信息”中选",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_003_textile_application_flow_b011",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          90.0,
          420.0369567871094,
          505.18585205078125,
          441.4897155761719
        ],
        "page": 1
      },
      "text": "择“十大品类”，每个品类限报两件产品，例如“时尚流行产品”",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_003_textile_application_flow_b012",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          90.0,
          454.10321044921875,
          505.18853759765625,
          470.05322265625
        ],
        "page": 1
      },
      "text": "品类每家企业限报两件产品，若还有产品待申报，请改选其",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_003_textile_application_flow_b013",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          90.0,
          485.30322265625,
          153.948486328125,
          501.25323486328125
        ],
        "page": 1
      },
      "text": "他品类。",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_003_textile_application_flow_b014",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          122.04000091552734,
          516.5032348632812,
          505.19000244140625,
          532.4531860351562
        ],
        "page": 1
      },
      "text": "下一步，上传申报企业和产品相关附件；完成后点击“提",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_003_textile_application_flow_b015",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          90.0,
          547.7032470703125,
          505.18853759765625,
          563.6531982421875
        ],
        "page": 1
      },
      "text": "交”按钮。如需申报多件产品，请重复以上操作。在左侧导",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_003_textile_application_flow_b016",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          90.0,
          576.0369873046875,
          505.3035888671875,
          597.4896850585938
        ],
        "page": 1
      },
      "text": "航栏的“申报管理”中，可查看已申报产品的审核状态和流程",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_003_textile_application_flow_b017",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          90.0,
          610.103271484375,
          137.9890899658203,
          626.05322265625
        ],
        "page": 1
      },
      "text": "进度。",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_003_textile_application_flow_b018",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          122.04000091552734,
          641.3079223632812,
          218.02908325195312,
          657.4971923828125
        ],
        "page": 1
      },
      "text": "三、样品寄送",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_003_textile_application_flow_b019",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          122.04000091552734,
          672.5032348632812,
          505.1835632324219,
          688.4531860351562
        ],
        "page": 1
      },
      "text": "申报产品通过初审后，系统将自动给企业联系人发送关",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_003_textile_application_flow_b020",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          90.0,
          700.8369750976562,
          505.19000244140625,
          722.2896728515625
        ],
        "page": 1
      },
      "text": "于寄送样品的短信。请接到通知的企业登录申报系统，在“申",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_003_textile_application_flow_b021",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          90.0,
          732.0369873046875,
          511.19000244140625,
          753.4896850585938
        ],
        "page": 1
      },
      "text": "报管理”中查看申报进度，并下载系统自动生成的“申报书”，",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 9.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_003_textile_application_flow_b022",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          295.20001220703125,
          780.751953125,
          300.1750183105469,
          794.1347045898438
        ],
        "page": 2
      },
      "text": "2",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_003_textile_application_flow_b023",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          90.0,
          79.70321655273438,
          505.1811828613281,
          95.6532211303711
        ],
        "page": 2
      },
      "text": "打印后在首页、真实性承诺页及骑缝处加盖企业公章后回传",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_003_textile_application_flow_b024",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          90.0,
          108.03694915771484,
          505.19000244140625,
          129.4897003173828
        ],
        "page": 2
      },
      "text": "系统，并将实物样品（至少1 套，以最小销售单元为准；若",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_003_textile_application_flow_b025",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          90.0,
          142.1032257080078,
          505.1850280761719,
          158.05322265625
        ],
        "page": 2
      },
      "text": "为服装产品，建议整套搭配寄送）及加盖企业公章的纸质版",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_003_textile_application_flow_b026",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          90.0,
          173.30322265625,
          281.9845886230469,
          189.2532196044922
        ],
        "page": 2
      },
      "text": "申报材料寄送至如下地址。",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_003_textile_application_flow_b027",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          122.04000091552734,
          201.63694763183594,
          505.19000244140625,
          223.08970642089844
        ],
        "page": 2
      },
      "text": "寄送地址：北京市朝阳区霞光里15 号霄云中心211 室",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_003_textile_application_flow_b028",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          90.0,
          232.83694458007812,
          449.86102294921875,
          254.28970336914062
        ],
        "page": 2
      },
      "text": "（100026），十大类纺织创新产品工作办公室（收）",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_003_textile_application_flow_b029",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          122.04000091552734,
          266.907958984375,
          218.02908325195312,
          283.0971984863281
        ],
        "page": 2
      },
      "text": "四、样品退回",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_003_textile_application_flow_b030",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          122.04000091552734,
          298.10321044921875,
          505.18414306640625,
          314.05322265625
        ],
        "page": 2
      },
      "text": "寄送样品默认不予退回，若产品过于贵重或其他原因需",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_003_textile_application_flow_b031",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          90.0,
          326.43695068359375,
          505.1843566894531,
          347.88970947265625
        ],
        "page": 2
      },
      "text": "要退回，请在“产品申请退回”页面进行登记，并填写申请退",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_003_textile_application_flow_b032",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          90.0,
          360.50323486328125,
          505.1894226074219,
          376.4532470703125
        ],
        "page": 2
      },
      "text": "回原因；由于该项工作不收取任何费用，申请退回的样品默",
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "attributes": {
        "font_bold": false,
        "font_size": 15.949999809265137
      },
      "block_id": "real_general_003_textile_application_flow_b033",
      "level": null,
      "source_anchor": {
        "bbox": [
          90.0,
          391.7032165527344,
          185.98757934570312,
          407.6532287597656
        ],
        "page": 2
      },
      "text": "认顺丰到付。",
      "type": "paragraph"
    }
  ],
